'''Nkik clan''' was a [[Jawa/Legends|Jawa]] clan. [[Wimateeka]] was the leader of this clan. [[Het Nkik/Legends|Het]] & [[Jek Nkik]] were also members of this clan.

==History==
In [[1 ABY/Legends|1 ABY]] the clan was attacked by [[Human/Legends|Humans]] and aliens and several Jawas were killed. Wimateeka hired a well armed individual to destroy the base of their enemies.<ref name="SWG:JK">{{SWGcite|exp=AED|type=terminal||Jawa Killers}} on Tatooine</ref>

On another occasion, Wimateeka contracted a number of hunters to eliminate wild animals that were attacking his clan's supply of [[Hubba gourd/Legends|hubba gourds]].<ref name="SWG:HGR">{{SWGcite|exp=AED|type=terminal||Hubba Gourd Raiders}} on Tatooine</ref>

At one time during the [[Galactic Civil War/Legends|Galactic Civil War]], the clan's [[Sandcrawler/Legends|sandcrawler]] accommodated an [[Unidentified Rebel agent (droid builder)|unidentified Rebel operative]] who learnt the art of droid crafting under the aegis of Wimateeka.<ref name="Star Wars: DroidWorks">''[[Star Wars: DroidWorks]]''</ref>

